These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, domino, mah-jongg
City: nizza, new-york, boston, berlin
House: townhouse, farmhouse, tower, gothic-revival
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, white, fuchsia
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 2. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
 3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the tower house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the farmhouse house is the person playing domino##1
 8. the person who likes white is in an even position##4
 9. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person traveling to berlin##2
10. the person playing canasta is the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person traveling to boston is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | domino  | canasta    | mah-jongg    | scrabble   |
| City   | new-york     | nizza   | boston       | berlin    |
| House   | farmhouse | townhouse | gothic-revival    | tower |
| Color           | orange | fuchsia       | turquise | white     |

