.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, rat, turtle
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, aquamarine, purple, blue
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, cola, hot-chocolate, juice
4 different games are played: domino, monopoly, bridge, chess
 1. the person who likes blue is in an even position##4
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking water##1
 5. the person playing chess is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Pet          | fish  | guinea-pig    | rat     | turtle       |
| Color         | purple | blue | light-blue   | aquamarine |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | water   | cola   | juice    |
| Game         | bridge | chess  | domino | monopoly   |

