.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, airplane, car, roller
City: london, venice, marseilles, new-york
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, classical, blues, reggae
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold, lily, aconite
 1. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 2. the fan of classical is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 3. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is the person traveling to new-york##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is in an even position##4
 9. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of pop##1
10. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the car##1
11. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Transport      | bus | car   | roller    | airplane      |
| City           | marseilles | london | venice | new-york     |
| Music-Genre   | classical      | reggae   | pop   | blues |
| Flower           | aconite         | orchid       | lily  | marigold       |

