.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, july, september
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, american, german
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, chef, teacher, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, electronic, funk, salsa
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is the brazilian##1
 2. the teacher is on the left of the analyst##1
 3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 4. the chef is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is the fan of salsa##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 8. the canadian is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the fan of funk is the chef##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the analyst##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is the german##1
12. the german is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | september       | july   | january   | november   |
| Nationality       | canadian        | german | brazilian    | american       |
| Job      | software-developer | chef    | teacher  | analyst |
| Music-Genre      | electronic  | funk  | folk | salsa    |

