.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, blues, disco, jazz
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, rat, fish
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, scrabble, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, argentine, italian, brazilian
 1. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the owner of the rat is between the japanese and the fan of jazz##2
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the argentine##1
 4. the person playing canasta is the fan of electronic##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 6. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
 7. the fan of blues is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the owner of the rat is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
11. the brazilian is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
12. the owner of the fish is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Music-Genre    | disco    | jazz      | electronic          | blues    |
| Pet   | pony | fish       | rat | cat |
| Game     | chess     | scrabble      | canasta     | snooker |
| Nationality   | argentine   | brazilian | italian        | japanese   |

