The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, singing, drawing, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, adventure, spy, martial-arts
City: new-york, london, hamburg, marseilles
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 5. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person watching adventure movies##2
 7. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Transport      | subway  | quad-bike    | trike       | motorbike       |
| Hobby          | writing    | drawing | singing | chess     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | spy        | martial-arts    | adventure   |
| City   | new-york  | hamburg      | marseilles    | london |

