 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 9. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
