.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, nectarine, banana, grapefruit
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, tea, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, lacrosse, snowboarding, cricket
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, accountant, bartender, lawyer
 1. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
 2. the scientist is between the lawyer and the bartender##2
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 4. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 7. the bartender is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 8. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the scientist is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person drinking milk##2
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the scientist##1
11. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food         | nectarine  | banana    | blueberry    | grapefruit |
| Beverage   | tea   | 7up       | milk  | juice    |
| Sport   | water-polo | lacrosse | snowboarding | cricket   |
| Job           | bartender    | scientist        | lawyer   | accountant    |

