 7. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 8. the scientist is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
