The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, scooter, boat
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is between the person driving the boat and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person driving the boat is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
11. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Birthday      | april      | may      | june           | november |
| Game           | scrabble | backgammon | go | monopoly        |
| Flower   | iris      | tulip  | amaryllis          | balloon-flower      |
| Transport         | boat       | scooter    | snowmobile       | airplane       |

