The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, thriller, fantasy, scientific
 1. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 4. the person watching scientific movies is between the fan of punk and the person who likes coral##2
 5. the owner of the snake is the fan of techno##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 9. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of gospel##1
11. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
13. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Pet    | goldfish    | goat        | snake   | dog      |
