|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport      | car   | motorbike   | boat     | jet-ski   |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | aristoff       | bluemaster | tiparillo |
| Hobby           | writing     | reading   | card-games     | singing     |
| Birthday         | november | march | july   | april |

