.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, zinnia, aconite
House: futuristic, wooden, gothic-revival, modern
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, march, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, quad-bike, snowmobile, ship
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the modern house##1
 7. the wooden house is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
12. the futuristic house is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Flower      | zinnia       | bellflower | daffodil        | aconite        |
| House         | modern | gothic-revival       | futuristic | wooden |
| Birthday   | april     | october        | september    | march      |
| Transport         | quad-bike     | snowmobile    | ship | train   |

