.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, tiparillo, pall-mall, alhambra
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, police-officer, electrician, manager
City: hannover, venice, nizza, marseilles
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, july, march
 1. the alhambra-smoker is the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is between the entrepreneur and the manager##2
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the police-officer##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 8. the manager is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
10. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4
11. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | tiparillo      | oliveros | alhambra     | pall-mall        |
| Job   | electrician | manager  | police-officer     | entrepreneur |
| City         | venice    | hannover | nizza      | marseilles |
| Birthday     | march | august     | july | february       |

 